>\n<digg:commentCount>69</digg:commentCount>\n</item>\n<item>\n<title>Before the iPhone there was Newton</title>\n<link>http://digg.com/apple/Before_the_iPhone_there_was_Newton</link>\n<description>We were all wowed by the iPhone last week, but back in 1993 Apple introduced a revolutionary product called Newton that defined the PDA industry.  Watch this Newton &quot;getting started&quot; video from 1993 and wonder why your 2006 PDA can''t do half the things Newton revolutionized fourteen years ago!</description>\n<pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2007 21:30:02 GMT</pubDate>\n<guid isPermaLink="true">http://digg.com/apple/Before_the_iPhone_there_was_Newton</guid>\n<digg:diggCount>641</digg:diggCount>\n<digg:submitter><digg:username>lonseidman</digg:username><digg:userimage>http://digg.com/img/user-medium/user-default.png</digg:userimage></digg:submitter>\n<digg:category>Apple</digg:category>\n<digg:commentCount>86</digg:commentCount>\n</item>\n<item>\n<title>Some new features for Digg v4?</title>\n<link>http://digg.com/design/Some_new_features_for_Digg_v4</link>\n<description>Personal Comment Colors, Mark As “Digg Effect” &amp; Then Auto-Mirror The Story, Ability to reply to a reply and more options for the comment area, More Categories, and other stuff. If anyone has more options they would like to see, post them and I will add them to the list. Maybe some of our wishes will come true in v4 if Kevin likes the ideas.</description>\n<pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2007 21:10:02 GMT</pubDate>\n<guid isPermaLink="true">http://digg.com/design/Some_new_features_for_Digg_v4</guid>\n<digg:diggCount>55</digg:diggCount>\n<digg:submitter><digg:username>sicc</digg:username><digg:userimage>http://digg.com/userimages/s/i/c/sicc/medium5012.jpg</digg:userimage></digg:submitter>\n<digg:category>Design</digg:category>\n<digg:commentCount>13</digg:commentCount>\n</item>\n<item>\n<title>10 Responses in the iPhone and Apple''s Defense</title>\n<link>http://digg.com/apple/10_Responses_in_the_iPhone_and_Apple_s_